          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h1>We built this from scratch. No investors. No shortcuts. Just two siblings, a vision, and a warehouse floor. we packed the first orders by hand. Slept next to the inventory. Now it’s global. But it wasn’t always. This is for the ones who’ve been watching.</h1>",
